Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shout. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sealed Blaze Maiden\NFace Off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruka, here are the documents for those \Nwho will be conducting prayers this weekend. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have Miss Mirei validate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The owners of the land I purified the other day \Nwish to give Miss Mirei something as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What would she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei likes black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruka, a new client wishes for both of you \Nto come and visit them in the Ezo region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei does not travel by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Shall we be on our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, you don't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to go to Ezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My! For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try guarana soda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,6 damage. Just as I'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was educational for all of you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the lesson was that we shouldn't talk \Nabout other things in the middle of a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader shouldn't need a warning, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, you constantly misrepresent me, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want guarana soda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "guarana"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a yellow fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NIt's a yellow fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this your chance to get closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, that's not what I'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After considering the matter in my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect you came here in order \Nto get closer to that girl, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! Shut up about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place where you can get guarana soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This says they're holding an Ezo Fair, \Nat the Nagoya Station building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I was just wondering if that thing \Nabout the Ezo Fair was true or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... lemme see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe make it a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a minute!\NMake it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, please!\NMake it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I must get Ms. Haruka's permission first!\NMake it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NMake it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because...\NMake it a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right, Ms. Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See how happy Miss Mirei looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're talking about dates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you have permission to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wish for is Miss Mirei's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even lend you the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go enjoy yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Mr. Momoyama, would you like \Nto open your window, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a short flight, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Momoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, that was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The station building \Nappears to be across the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we get the soda, then return home at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? We just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruka will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pancake Fish 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I live for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what? Haruka scolds me, \Ntelling me that I eat too many sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so annoying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not merely a sign she is \Nthinking of your well-being, Miss Mirei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Even you parrot the same things \Nthat those adults say, Mr. Momoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray, it's the tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? Not even Haruka \Nknows this secret of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the pancake fish's tail best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess either end is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Prefers tail of pancake fish
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, lending out someone else's car... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I did get that person's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Had that person known who you were \Nlending it to, you wouldn't have gotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I love, love, LOVE the smell of nail polish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what? \NHaruka scolds me with, "Don't sniff that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, the precious charm Haruka gave me \Nand said I should never, ever lose? I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It couldn't be in my pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How?! How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected you were a person with a tendency \Nto put all sorts of things into your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes, that's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold Out, Thank You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We took too many side trips first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not even a magician \Ncould predict they would sell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd swear you know everything \Nabout me, Mr. Momoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine without the soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... but if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...could we have fun... for a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! That just startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ezo Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back...\NEzo Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ezo Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Momoyama, um, I'm sorry that \NI grabbed you like that. Were you startled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart is beating incredibly fast, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that \Nyou have trouble with loud noises?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a good method for times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to the plush toys section?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hug it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this lets you share your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is another secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at my age, I still sleep with a teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's no ordinary bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, really important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when I was sick in bed with a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother saved his allowance to buy it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hugged it the way \Nhe told me to, I felt more at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, because of that, \Nnow I'm unable to sleep without the bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...had a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,While he's a bit strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and people at the house always used to scold him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he's really funny, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He joined me in my pranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and did stuff like make holes \Nin the walls of the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,which got him a big, big scolding from Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji, you go quiet so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my conversation bore you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been super-polite with me all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...I am your servant, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, since you're my servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll do what I ask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is here okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you'll quit being so polite to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn. I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I discard a Jake from my hand, and ride Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With its skill, I call Matt from the Soul \Nto the middle of the back row.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I Soul Charge with Deryck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Namorkahr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I take a Swayanbuh from my deck \Nand add it to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Namorkahr attacks your Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a Recusal Hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn. I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I discard a Brothers' Soul from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and ride Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With its skill, I put Matt \Nin the Soul, and draw one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Halibadra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Halibadra attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruce attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical trigger--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a fist pump, didn't you?\NCritical trigger--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a breach of etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't behave in a way \Nthat will bewilder your opponent."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that one of Daybreak's principles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka and I decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Miss Mirei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei, what is \Nyour opinion of that etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to disturb my emotions \Nwith irrelevant conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it is nobody's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply wanted to know \Nyour feelings about it, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has asked me such a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...other than my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What would he ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd often say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"To hell with manners!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel that way, too, Miss Mirei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, while poses like fist pumps are bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...occasionally, there are times \Nwhen I feel like laughing gently, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can laugh together, \Nthat will let us be a little closer as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be closer friends, with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on who wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you really will \Nquit being so polite with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But only if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bavsargra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I arm Bavsargra with Swayanbuh \Nas Left Deity Arms. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bavsargra attacks your Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a change... in the air around her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get swallowed up by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With a boost from Ihsita, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sikshanya attacks your Vanguard.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Final Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden attacks Sikshanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden attacks Sikshanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates! I retire Ihsita!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"No guard," without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face is unreadable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruce attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With its skill, I restand \Nall rear-guards in the front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Double front trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The unease hasn't vanished... but!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep this up to force my way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With Swayanbuh's skill, \NBavsargra gets +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely nothing got through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I arm Bavsargra with Prithivih \Nas Right Deity Arms. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With Bavsargra's skill when armed with both cards,\N I retire all my opponent's front row rear-guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it gets an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She protected that rear-guard earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to reserve the back row unit \Nthat's boosting it here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With a boost from Ihsita, \NBavsargra attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei... were you...\NWith a boost from Ihsita, \NBavsargra attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,With the armed Prithivih's skill, \Nit gains +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...always like this?!\NWith the armed Prithivih's skill, \Nit gains +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive. Front trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It still won't go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Prithivih's other skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,by discarding this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I deal 1 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fun person, Mr. Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I might be, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I mean, I suppose so, Mirei. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a leaf stuck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, this turned into a real bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our assassins came scurrying back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they had such a horrible time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried following up on the places they'd fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it appears that something is headed our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.55,0:25:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.35,0:25:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your leader: Mirei!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.40,0:25:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce my card, \NSealed Blaze Maiden, Bavsargra.\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With Bavsargra, you can arm \Ntwo dedicated Order cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.01,0:26:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are: Sealed Blaze Sword, Prithivih, \Nand Sealed Blaze Shield, Swayanbuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.24,0:26:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By arming them, not only can you retire \Nall of your opponent's rear-guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.66,0:26:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you can even get an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.16,0:26:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With those two weapons, \Nyou'll knock down all the bad guys!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.29,0:26:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.28,0:26:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon\NGluttony 
